      "description": "Configuration-first v2 entity workflow. Live proof on 2026-03-06 confirmed that `/v2/entities` accepts array-style query params (`type[]`, `fields[]`), scalar `type` fails, and child types such as component/feature/subfeature require a parent relationship at create time in tested workspaces."
